{"tid":286435,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"饒戈平：一地兩檢勿政治化","createTime":"2017-06-16T15:05:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-16T15:12:16.000Z","uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c329d67775d1fdbcca81dfcb19b34828a22b6825","tid":286435,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T15:05:38.000Z","msg":"基本法委員會委員饒戈平表示，廣深港高鐵的一地兩檢安排，如果參考深圳灣案例，內地執法人員在西九總站，只會進行海關檢疫等技術性執法，不會全面實施內地法例。他認為，一地兩檢毋須修改基本法附件三，希望香港社會不要將事件政治化，嚇唬自己。<br />\n<br />\n饒戈平批評，部分人將一地兩檢視為香港向內地割讓土地，認為是概念錯誤，亦忽略香港實際地位。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E9%A5%92%E6%88%88%E5%B9%B3%E7%9B%B8%E4%BF%A1%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%B0%E5%85%A9%E6%AA%A2%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92%E5%8F%AF%E5%8F%83%E8%80%83%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E7%81%A3%E6%A1%88%E4%BE%8B-%E5%86%80%E5%8B%BF%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E5%8C%96-82914\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E9%25A5%2592%25E6%2588%2588%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E7%259B%25B8%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%258E%2592%25E5%258F%25AF%25E5%258F%2583%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E5%259C%25B3%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%25A1%2588%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E5%2586%2580%25E5%258B%25BF%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E5%258C%2596-82914&d=295Y0z%2FBbguxGBzpa06cgLZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=c597e9c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E9%A5%92%E6%88%88%E5%B9%B3%E7%9B%B8%E4%BF%A1%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%B0%E5%85%A9%E6%AA%A2%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92%E5%8F%AF%E5%8F%83%E8%80%83%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E7%81%A3%E6%A1%88%E4%BE%8B-%E5%86%80%E5%8B%BF%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E5%8C%96-82914</a>"},{"pid":"80d7412bc1c0ad479f1e56967a8808085f08d430","tid":286435,"uid":16742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T15:12:16.000Z","msg":"煩唔煩啲，一日到尾剩係識講唔好政治化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}